<item>
            <title>[LU-3253] MDT objects are not really MD objects</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3253</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is currently no reason for struct mdt_object to include a md_object when it can just use an lu_object instead. Same for struct mdt_device. Switching from md_object to lu_object saves 16 bytes and makes for more concise code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
